1
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,360
Yuanbao.

2
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,920
Keep acting.

3
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,880
Keep acting.

4
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:54,680
Come on.

5
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:55,920
I am here.

6
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,720
It seems I shouldn't have come here.

7
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,980
It's too late for you to realize that now.

8
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,300
Can I leave some memories behind?

9
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,000
I don't want to leave any memories.

10
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,079
If you want to leave something, leave yourself.

11
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,440
You can only get my body.

12
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,100
You won't get my heart.

13
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,060
We won't have a future.

14
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,040
Just let me go.

15
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:54,440
Fine, I can let you go.

16
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,720
But you must hug me before you go.

17
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,800
I am a sunset warrior after all.

18
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:03,280
If I hug you just because you ask me to.

19
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,480
Where is my pride?

20
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:05,920
You're lying.

21
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,810
You don't dare to hug me.

22
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:10,280
Which means you still have feelings for me.

23
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,440
Let me tell you.

24
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,840
If you reject me today.

25
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,520
You'll regret it for the rest of your life.

26
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,120
I won't hug you even if I regret it.

27
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:20,800
We can only blame destiny.

28
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,760
It's been 18 years.

29
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,520
It seems like this is the first time

30
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,840
I've looked into his eyes so closely.

31
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:58,320
At this moment, his eyes seem to hold the sea of stars.

32
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,920
Qingyun is so handsome.

33
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:07,440
I didn't know Qingyun was such a good actor.

34
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:28,920
Watch out!

35
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,320
Yuanbao.

36
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,920
Yuanbao.

37
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,040
Yuanbao.

38
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,640
What's wrong? Are you okay?

39
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:45,100
Hurry, call an ambulance!

40
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,480
Make the call!

41
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,800
Hurry!

42
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:48,600
Come on.

43
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,440
Be careful.

44
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,200
Slow down.

45
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,000
Yuanbao, don't be afraid.

46
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,159
We are going to the hospital right now.

47
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:54,159
Tell the teacher. Hurry!

48
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:54,560
Okay.

49
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,020
Hurry, call an ambulance!

50
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,560
Slow down.

51
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,120
Slow down.

52
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,520
Slow down.

53
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,120
Yuanbao.

54
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,240
Grandma.

55
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,360
Doctor, how is she?

56
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,580
How is it, Yuanbao?

57
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,720
Don't worry, we've checked everything.

58
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,120
Fortunately,

59
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,440
her eyeball was not injured.

60
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,800
Her brow bone and upper eyelid

61
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,320
were scratched by broken glass,

62
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,520
which is why she bled.

63
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,080
However, considering she is a girl,

64
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,610
we didn't give her stitches

65
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,800
for fear of leaving scars.

66
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,120
But we have treated her wound,

67
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,240
and it will heal properly.

68
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,200
But remember,

69
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:42,440
you must come to change the dressing every two days.

70
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,800
Most importantly, don't make big movements.

71
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,840
Otherwise, the wound won't heal well.

72
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:49,600
Doctor, it definitely won't leave a scar, right?

73
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:51,720
It's hard to say.

74
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,480
It depends on how you recover.

75
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,840
But we already have

76
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,560
scar removal technology.

77
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,680
Even if a little scar remains,

78
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,840
it can be treated with technology.

79
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:04,920
Doctor, can I take this gauze off first?

80
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:07,570
I have an important performance tonight.

81
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,920
After my competition is over,

82
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:11,320
can I put this gauze back on?

83
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,040
Well,

84
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:14,000
why are you still thinking about the performance?

85
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,200
If it weren't for this performance,

86
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,000
would your eye have gotten hurt?

87
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,120
That won't do.

88
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,320
If you take it off now, the wound will tear,

89
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,400
and it will get infected.

90
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,520
You should also try not to make big movements

91
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,720
or facial expressions around the eyes.

92
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,680
Yuanbao's mom,

93
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,440
I'm really sorry.

94
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,440
The child was injured at school.

95
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,770
We really didn't expect

96
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,960
that there would be a problem with the school auditorium lights.

97
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,640
The school will cover the medical expenses.

98
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,640
I'm really sorry.

99
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:39,120
Mr. Tian, we can't blame you.

100
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,720
This was just an accident.

101
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,480
Thank you.

102
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,340
Thank you for understanding.

103
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,400
I'll go prescribe the medicine first.

104
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,480
Family members, please remember

105
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,520
to come and pick up the medicine with the prescription later.

106
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,400
Okay. Thank you, doctor.

107
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:53,520
Mom. Grandma.

108
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,240
Listen to the doctor.

109
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,560
Fortunately, your eyes weren't injured.

110
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,920
Don't think about anything right now.

111
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:01,360
Recovering your eyes is the most important thing.

112
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,640
Mr. Tian, Yuanbao...

113
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,000
I understand.

114
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,570
Her health comes first.

115
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:10,240
Yuanbao, just focus on recovering now.

116
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,760
Don't worry about the class competition.

117
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:14,520
The classes you miss these days,

118
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,440
I will ask the teachers to help you catch up.

119
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,480
Get well soon.

120
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,440
Mr. Tian, about tonight's performance,

121
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,840
how are you going to arrange it?

122
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,500
I called Meng Jingu's family.

123
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,400
He has some family issues.

124
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,000
Now you are injured too.

125
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:29,840
We have to withdraw from this competition.

126
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:32,120
It's fine. There will be other chances.

127
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,760
This drama competition,

128
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,200
our whole class

129
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:37,480
has prepared carefully for a long time.

130
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,440
It's tonight.

131
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,800
If because of me,

132
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,800
causing everyone to quit the competition,

133
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,640
I would really be to blame.

134
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,780
I understand how you feel.

135
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,740
But there is nothing we can do.

136
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,440
Mutou.

137
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,320
Can you and Xing Yaqi

138
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,800
perform on stage instead of us?

139
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,000
I don't want to go.

140
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,840
I want to stay and take care of you.

141
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,640
Didn't the doctor say I'm fine?

142
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:04,480
Besides, the scenes of Joker and Zixia

143
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,730
only you and Xing Yaqi have practiced.

144
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,320
Now that Meng Jingu and I

145
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,720
both can't participate.

146
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:11,240
How can we bear

147
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:13,800
to see our classmates' efforts go to waste?

148
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,560
Just consider it as me begging you, okay?

149
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,280
Go.

150
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,760
That's a way.

151
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:22,220
Mu Qingyun, why don't you think about it?

152
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,840
Didn't you tell me before

153
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,460
that you want to act again?

154
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,460
You told the teacher you wanted to act again.

155
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:32,039
Qingyun, since this is about the class,

156
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,720
you should help if you can.

157
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,960
This way you can also

158
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:37,159
let Yuanbao recover with peace of mind.

159
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,039
There is one thing

160
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,320
I want to ask of you.

161
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,240
Tell me.

162
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,040
Can I go take a look?

163
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,480
You still want to go in this condition?

164
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,400
Can I?

165
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,160
Well, since they want to go so badly,

166
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:02,160
let's go with them.

167
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,040
I really don't know what to do with you.

168
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:07,200
Let's go.

169
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,330
Have you figured it out?

170
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,810
Where are you going?

171
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,480
Jingu.

172
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,400
This kid.

173
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,600
Zhi Zun Bao.

174
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,680
Don't talk this nonsense to me.

175
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:34,610
I said you've got the wrong person.

176
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,620
This Purple Gold Bell,

177
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,040
how do you explain it?

178
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:41,840
Zhi Zun Bao, prepare to die!

179
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,200
Great Sage Equal to Heaven, Sun Wukong.

180
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,400
I am Zixia.

181
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:03,840
My true love is a peerless hero.

182
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:09,360
One day, he will wear golden armor

183
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,770
and ride on seven-colored clouds to marry me.

184
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,120
I guessed the beginning,

185
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,440
but I couldn't guess the ending.

186
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,480
Zixia.

187
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,040
Okay.

188
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,040
Go up, Yuanbao.

189
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:06,440
Go up, Yuanbao.

190
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,300
Go up, Yuanbao.

191
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,560
Let's go.

192
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:15,480
Yuanbao, let's go up together.

193
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,240
You must be careful.

194
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:17,640
Let's go.

195
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:19,000
Take good care of her.

196
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:26,680
Yuanbao.

197
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,600
Yuanbao.

198
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,690
You are awesome.

199
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,600
Come on, let's take a bow together.

200
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,320
Okay.

201
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,160
Yuanbao.

202
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:05,840
What's wrong?

203
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:06,980
Yuanbao! Yuanbao!

204
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,420
Yuanbao, don't go.

205
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,280
Yuanbao, you're awake.

206
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,080
Yuanbao is awake.

207
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,530
How are you feeling?

208
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,560
Why am I at home?

209
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:54,140
Where else would you be if not at home?

210
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:55,840
Yuanbao.

211
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,440
You're awake.

212
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:58,920
Do your eyes still hurt?

213
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,960
Yuanbao, are you still dizzy?

214
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,200
I'm fine.

215
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,400
Since when have I been here?

216
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,560
Wasn't I in the auditorium?

217
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:07,560
Don't even mention it.

218
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:08,920
You scared us to death.

219
00:13:09,160 --> 00:13:09,560
Yeah.

220
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:12,000
The doctor said you've been too tired lately,

221
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,720
and you didn't eat anything all day,

222
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:15,180
so you had low blood sugar.

223
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,200
You passed out in the auditorium.

224
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:19,760
Here, drink some brown sugar water.

225
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:20,400
Here.

226
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:21,530
I'll do it, Grandma.

227
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:23,170
Blow on it for her. It's hot.

228
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:27,560
Drink slowly.

229
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,600
Drink more brown sugar water.

230
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,400
Drink up.

231
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,160
After dinner, have some fruit.

232
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,490
We need to keep up with your nutrition.

233
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,880
What time is it?

234
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,200
It's past eleven.

235
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:47,290
You've been sleeping since you came back yesterday.

236
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,320
I slept so well.

237
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:55,840
Grandma made you

238
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,700
your favorite braised pork ribs.

239
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,840
Get up quickly.

240
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,720
Get up, wash up, and let's eat.

241
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,090
Do you want some?

242
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,680
You scared me. Get up.

243
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,280
How are you? Are you feeling okay?

244
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,400
Slow down, slow down, slow down.

245
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,240
Slow down.

246
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:22,440
Slow down.

247
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,520
Come, sweetie.

248
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,920
Drink some soup.

249
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,840
It has medicinal herbs in it.

250
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:28,480
It's specially for your eyes.

251
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,360
Drink up.

252
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:34,080
Good.

253
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:38,520
By the way, Mutou.

254
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:42,160
Thanks for agreeing to perform on stage.

255
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,640
If it weren't for you,

256
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:47,770
everyone's hard work would have been wasted.

257
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:48,960
All right.

258
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,880
Let bygones be bygones.

259
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:51,920
From now on, you two

260
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:54,050
must focus on your studies and behave.

261
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,240
No more thinking about things other than studying.

262
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,040
Do you hear me?

263
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:57,960
Got it, Mom.

264
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:58,880
I know.

265
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,600
What are you laughing at?

266
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:11,080
Try covering one eye.

267
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,530
You'd definitely be worse than me.

268
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:16,720
Having only one eye is so uncomfortable.

269
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,380
I can't walk straight,

270
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:20,200
can't pick up food,

271
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,760
and I feel dizzy.

272
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,530
Let's see if you'll join the fun next time.

273
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:27,360
You're never this active when it comes to studying.

274
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,560
But for other things,

275
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,490
you're always the first to rush in.

276
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,600
This is a lesson for you.

277
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:36,640
Grandma, I'm the victim here too, okay?

278
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,740
The light exploded suddenly.

279
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,700
I couldn't have seen that coming.

280
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,760
It's really not my fault this time.

281
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,090
What is this called?

282
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,400
It's an unexpected disaster.

283
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:49,320
Grandma.

284
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,120
Actually,

285
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:54,220
Yuanbao got hurt trying to save me this time.

286
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:55,800
Really?

287
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:59,360
If Yuanbao hadn't pushed me,

288
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,080
I would be the one injured now.

289
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:05,840
Don't listen to his nonsense.

290
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,040
I,

291
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:10,800
I just pushed him subconsciously.

292
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:12,840
I'm not as great as he says.

293
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,400
Don't flatter yourself.

294
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:15,720
Alright,

295
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:17,920
it was Yuanbao who saved you.

296
00:16:18,040 --> 00:16:20,440
Exactly. We're a family.

297
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:21,650
Don't be a stranger.

298
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,160
Qingyun, come, eat.

299
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,440
Thank you, Grandma.

300
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,080
By the way,

301
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,760
your eye is injured,

302
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:30,840
what about your missed schoolwork?

303
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,400
Qingyun.

304
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:34,520
Forget it.

305
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:37,620
You probably can't help her catch up either.

306
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:40,280
What's the name of your desk mate?

307
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:41,200
Something Jin.

308
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,320
Meng Jingu.

309
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:44,160
Right, right.

310
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:46,080
Isn't he really good at studying?

311
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,940
How about you ask him to tutor you?

312
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:52,840
I already bother him too much.

313
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,450
It's not a good idea.

314
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:55,480
True,

315
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:58,060
he probably doesn't have that much time.

316
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,360
How about I try?

317
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,480
Give me a break.

318
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,599
What are you laughing at?

319
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:12,290
Even if you dared to tutor me, I wouldn't dare listen.

320
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:15,079
I'm afraid you'll drag me down to last place.

321
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,530
That's ridiculous.

322
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,210
Just because you said that,

323
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:21,680
I have to tutor you.

324
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:24,720
If I can memorize all the questions the teacher explains in class

325
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:26,050
and explain them to you,

326
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:28,660
how about you treat me to fried chicken legs?

327
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:32,240
That's a good idea. Improve together.

328
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,760
Then you'd better work hard.

329
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,290
If you teach Yuanbao wrong,

330
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,530
you'll be punished.

331
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:38,040
Okay.

332
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:41,400
It's a deal. Pinky promise.

333
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:42,620
Pinky promise.

334
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,720
Don't regret it.

335
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:45,080
We'll see who regrets it.

336
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:47,480
I'm definitely eating that fried chicken.

337
00:17:48,520 --> 00:17:50,080
Grandma and I are witnesses.

338
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,600
Neither of you can back out.

339
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:52,960
Hurry, eat.

340
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,600
The food is getting cold.

341
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,840
You didn't rest well at home,

342
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:06,100
and sneaked out alone.

343
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:08,240
Are you feeling sad

344
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:09,720
because you couldn't perform on stage?

345
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:11,120
Not exactly.

346
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:12,820
Then what's wrong?

347
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,120
Mutou,

348
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:16,320
tell me honestly,

349
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,600
am I

350
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,480
a really annoying person?

351
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,640
Why ask that suddenly?

352
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:24,960
Nothing.

353
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:28,240
I just feel that since Meng Jingu

354
00:18:28,280 --> 00:18:29,520
came to our class

355
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:31,680
and became my desk mate,

356
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:34,480
I seem to be always bothering him.

357
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,800
I ask him questions I don't know,

358
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:39,660
and ask him about homework I can't remember.

359
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:41,800
I tried so hard, but in the end,

360
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,480
I just kept

361
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,880
holding others back.

362
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:52,440
He's not as good as you say.

363
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:56,020
And you're not as bad as you think.

364
00:18:57,120 --> 00:18:59,560
You've made great progress lately, you know?

365
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:01,040
Your grades are improving,

366
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:03,000
and your New Concept Essay was so good.

367
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:05,040
I also know that to play Zixia,

368
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:07,800
you stayed up half the night memorizing lines.

369
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:12,260
How do you know I stayed up half the night memorizing lines?

370
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,000
Grandma told me.

371
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,760
Don't let one thing

372
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:21,570
make you doubt yourself, okay?

373
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,640
How can I not doubt myself?

374
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:27,000
Do you know why Meng Jingu

375
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:28,760
didn't show up in the end?

376
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:31,720
Do you know why?

377
00:19:33,520 --> 00:19:34,520
I don't know,

378
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:35,760
but I think

379
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:38,320
he probably hates me.

380
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:39,960
Thinking about it,

381
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:43,040
he might regret rehearsing with me

382
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:45,920
and lost confidence in me.

383
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:49,400
Thinking it's better to give up

384
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:51,880
than to lose face on stage.

385
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:55,960
Otherwise, why didn't he answer

386
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,400
after I called him so many times?

387
00:19:59,120 --> 00:20:00,240
Yuanbao.

388
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:02,120
Actually,

389
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:04,400
he could have just told me.

390
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:08,280
If he told me, I would understand.

391
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:13,200
Don't be sad suddenly.

392
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:14,680
The doctor said

393
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,560
you can't cry now.

394
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,240
Listen to me,

395
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:22,320
you are really, really excellent.

396
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,960
You just haven't realized it yourself.

397
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:29,560
Although I don't like Meng Jingu,

398
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:33,000
and I'm also angry that he stood you up,

399
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:34,440
but I don't think he would

400
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:35,970
do something so classless.

401
00:20:37,560 --> 00:20:39,720
Maybe something really happened to him,

402
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,520
so he couldn't answer your calls

403
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:43,080
or make it to the competition.

404
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:44,360
But the next day,

405
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:46,170
he acted like nothing happened

406
00:20:46,320 --> 00:20:47,560
and went to school.

407
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,880
Ruirui told me

408
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:52,960
he didn't look like he had been through anything.

409
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:55,240
Facing the gossiping from classmates,

410
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,560
he didn't say a word.

411
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:58,080
It was as if this

412
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:59,680
never even happened.

413
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:02,680
Don't worry.

414
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,240
When I have time later,

415
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:05,900
I'll go ask him what happened.

416
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:08,040
How about this?

417
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:09,640
Next time I see Meng Jingu,

418
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,780
I'll beat him up

419
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:12,040
to vent your anger.

420
00:21:12,840 --> 00:21:13,760
No.

421
00:21:15,360 --> 00:21:17,640
Why? Hearing I'm going to beat him up

422
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,780
makes you feel bad?

423
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,960
Not really.

424
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:22,600
Since this is over,

425
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:24,450
let's not mention it again.

426
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:27,480
From now on, I'll just bother him less.

427
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,960
Open your own homework.

428
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:54,440
Look, there are actually many ways

429
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,560
to solve this problem.

430
00:21:55,560 --> 00:21:57,020
The method you used before

431
00:21:57,280 --> 00:21:58,610
was quite complicated.

432
00:21:58,800 --> 00:22:00,120
I have a simpler way

433
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,120
to solve it.

434
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:02,560
Look, this...

435
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:08,210
What are you looking at?

436
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,960
How did you suddenly get so smart?

437
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:38,560
Your physics grades are usually so bad.

438
00:22:38,560 --> 00:22:40,600
How did you suddenly get a flash of inspiration today

439
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:41,860
and make so much sense?

440
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,680
Well, I...

441
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:49,240
I was afraid I wouldn't be able to explain it to you clearly,

442
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:51,700
so I listened very carefully in class today.

443
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:55,120
If you had been like this before,

444
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:57,120
your grades would have improved long ago.

445
00:22:57,120 --> 00:22:59,920
You wouldn't have worse grades than me every time.

446
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:02,520
I like it this way.

447
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:06,100
I can't be bothered to talk to you.

448
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:25,760
Yuanbao,

449
00:23:26,600 --> 00:23:27,840
how is your injury?

450
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,760
Why haven't you gone back to rest?

451
00:23:37,760 --> 00:23:38,600
Jingu.

452
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:41,600
When I went to find Yuanbao on the day of the competition,

453
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:43,400
before I had time to explain to her,

454
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:45,760
she was injured and sent to the hospital.

455
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:47,240
Thank you, Xinrui.

456
00:23:47,600 --> 00:23:49,860
For making a special trip for me that day.

457
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:51,160
I couldn't even help you.

458
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,960
I already feel very bad about it.

459
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:55,600
How about I find another time

460
00:23:55,840 --> 00:23:57,160
to help you explain to Yuanbao?

461
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:57,880
No need.

462
00:23:58,160 --> 00:23:59,560
I'll find an opportunity

463
00:23:59,560 --> 00:24:01,090
to explain to her in person.

464
00:24:02,080 --> 00:24:02,880
Okay.

465
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:07,960
Are you still mad at your dad?

466
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,730
He's just too dictatorial.

467
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,000
Since I was young,

468
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:15,770
I've been controlled by him like a puppet.

469
00:24:16,120 --> 00:24:16,760
Forget it.

470
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:18,700
Let's not talk about this.

471
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,080
I can understand you.

472
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:20,900
So just now,

473
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,560
I talked to your parents for a long time.

474
00:24:22,560 --> 00:24:23,760
They have promised that

475
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:25,360
as long as your grades remain stable,

476
00:24:25,360 --> 00:24:26,280
they will try their best to give you space

477
00:24:26,280 --> 00:24:27,480
and no longer interfere with your decisions.

478
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:28,160
Really?

479
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:28,960
Really.

480
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:31,620
It's just that they are elders after all.

481
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:34,880
They are too embarrassed to say some things in person,

482
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:37,140
so they asked me to pass this on to you.

483
00:24:39,040 --> 00:24:41,100
Don't be mad at your parents anymore.

484
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:43,480
They definitely mean well.

485
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:46,660
It's just that their methods might not be appropriate.

486
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:47,760
I know.

487
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:50,400
By the way,

488
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:54,200
you've been busy with the drama performance recently,

489
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:56,200
I was too embarrassed to bother you.

490
00:24:57,240 --> 00:24:59,320
Now that this is finally over,

491
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,240
can I ask you a favor?

492
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:02,440
Tell me.

493
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:05,760
As you know, I studied abroad for a year,

494
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:07,480
and fell behind on a lot of domestic courses.

495
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:09,010
You used to help me catch up.

496
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:10,560
Could I trouble you

497
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,240
to tutor me again in the future?

498
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,040
Of course.

499
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:14,000
Really?

500
00:25:14,280 --> 00:25:15,640
Then it's a promise.

501
00:25:18,280 --> 00:25:19,480
Signed and sealed.

502
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:22,880
Also,

503
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:25,100
your health is still very important.

504
00:25:25,320 --> 00:25:28,200
I've been busy lately and haven't had time to ask.

505
00:25:28,440 --> 00:25:29,770
How is your back injury?

506
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:33,040
I was in a hurry to find Yuanbao that day,

507
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,800
and accidentally fell again.

508
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:38,840
What's wrong? Do you need to go to the hospital?

509
00:25:39,080 --> 00:25:40,340
Don't worry, I'm fine.

510
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,240
I've applied some medicine,

511
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,970
and it will be fine in a few days.

512
00:25:43,120 --> 00:25:44,240
I'm sorry, Xinrui.

513
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:47,640
I was out of my mind with anger that day.

514
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:49,320
Knowing you have a back injury,

515
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:50,960
I still let you go to such a far place.

516
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,440
I...

517
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:53,240
Why are you being so polite to me?

518
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:54,840
Besides, even if you didn't ask,

519
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:57,440
I would still go to Yuanbao to explain clearly.

520
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,080
Don't worry.

521
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,640
Thank you, Xinrui.

522
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:04,880
Alright, stop thanking me so much.

523
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:07,000
Hurry up and drink your milk.

524
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,060
I'll go back first.

525
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:10,240
By the way.

526
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:13,290
Shall we start tutoring this weekend?

527
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:16,240
Bye.

528
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:52,240
Auntie, Grandmother.

529
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,840
I'm Yuanbao's desk mate.

530
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:56,040
My name is Meng Jingu.

531
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:57,520
I heard Yuanbao was injured.

532
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:58,580
So I came to see her.

533
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,960
So you are Meng Jingu.

534
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:02,040
I've heard Yuanbao mention you.

535
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:03,000
Oh, child.

536
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,400
You shouldn't have brought so much fruit.

537
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:05,920
Yes.

538
00:27:06,400 --> 00:27:08,680
Yuanbao, how are you feeling?

539
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,480
I'm much better.

540
00:27:13,080 --> 00:27:16,280
Luckily, it was just a scrape on the eyelid.

541
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:19,160
Come, sit on the sofa.

542
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,360
Yes, come in.

543
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:20,960
Come on.

544
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:21,840
Thank you, Grandma. Thank you, Auntie.

545
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:22,960
I'll cut some fruit for you.

546
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,200
Sit here.

547
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:36,440
How did you know my address?

548
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,040
I asked Tong Ruirui.

549
00:27:40,840 --> 00:27:41,600
I see.

550
00:27:42,080 --> 00:27:43,210
I'm sorry, Yuanbao.

551
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:44,560
That day,

552
00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:46,760
I didn't mean not to come.

553
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,280
It's okay.

554
00:27:50,160 --> 00:27:52,720
It's fine. I know you're busy.

555
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,120
It's okay.

556
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:57,720
Good thing Mutou and Yaqi were there.

557
00:27:58,280 --> 00:28:00,360
As long as everything went smoothly.

558
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:01,890
Actually, that day I...

559
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:03,780
You're only apologizing now.

560
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:05,580
Isn't it a bit too late?

561
00:28:07,120 --> 00:28:10,000
Yuanbao, I know no matter what I say,

562
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,040
wrong is wrong.

563
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:13,340
But please believe me,

564
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:15,380
I didn't mean not to come that day,

565
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:18,180
nor did I intentionally not contact you.

566
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:19,800
Here.

567
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:22,080
The fruit is cut. Have some.

568
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:23,760
Come, Jingu, eat some fruit.

569
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:24,820
Thank you, Auntie.

570
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,370
Thank you, Grandma.

571
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,440
Have you eaten?

572
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,540
I came straight after school.

573
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,320
Great.

574
00:28:31,760 --> 00:28:33,360
I cooked a lot of dishes today.

575
00:28:33,360 --> 00:28:34,360
Stay for dinner.

576
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:36,720
Yes, try Grandma's cooking.

577
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:38,080
No need.

578
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:44,690
What do you mean no need?

579
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:47,400
Jingu usually helps our Yuanbao a lot.

580
00:28:47,560 --> 00:28:49,440
And he even came especially to see Yuanbao today.

581
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,840
You must stay for dinner.

582
00:28:51,120 --> 00:28:53,160
These two kids are so insensitive.

583
00:28:54,040 --> 00:28:55,960
Auntie, I really don't need to.

584
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:56,760
Jingu,

585
00:28:57,320 --> 00:28:58,920
stay for dinner.

586
00:28:59,040 --> 00:29:00,500
Don't listen to those two.

587
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:01,240
Let's go.

588
00:29:01,280 --> 00:29:02,440
Let's go cook.

589
00:29:11,840 --> 00:29:12,640
Jingu,

590
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:16,000
I heard you're always first in your class.

591
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:18,920
More than that. First in the whole grade.

592
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:21,680
This kid,

593
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:24,080
so good-looking and smart.

594
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:25,280
Truly wonderful.

595
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:27,920
Eat more.

596
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:29,690
Thank you, Grandma.

597
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:32,600
Qingyun, you should learn from him

598
00:29:32,760 --> 00:29:34,490
and get first place for Mom too.

599
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,520
Okay, Mom.

600
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:38,160
I heard from Yuanbao

601
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:41,080
that you often help her with her homework at school.

602
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:43,970
Yuanbao is my desk mate. It's what I should do.

603
00:29:45,080 --> 00:29:46,920
Such a loyal kid.

604
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,240
Jingu,

605
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:50,360
Auntie has a favor to ask.

606
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:52,960
I don't know if it's convenient for you.

607
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:53,840
Auntie.

608
00:29:54,040 --> 00:29:54,970
Tell me, Auntie.

609
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:57,440
I'll try my best if I can do it.

610
00:29:58,920 --> 00:29:59,840
You see,

611
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:02,320
your final exams are coming up soon.

612
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:05,600
Yuanbao's grades weren't ideal to begin with.

613
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,120
Now her eyes are injured,

614
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:08,800
and she has fallen behind in her studies.

615
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:10,600
If you have time on the weekends,

616
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:11,840
could you come to our house

617
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:13,480
and tutor our Yuanbao?

618
00:30:14,560 --> 00:30:15,400
Is that okay?

619
00:30:23,040 --> 00:30:24,720
Just forget it if it's too much trouble.

620
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:26,120
Auntie was just asking.

621
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,400
Don't overthink it.

622
00:30:30,120 --> 00:30:32,600
Auntie, no problem. I have time.

623
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,520
That's great.

624
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:37,480
Come on.

625
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:39,400
Jingu, eat more.

626
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:44,760
Thank you.

627
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:49,440
Mom, I can also tutor Yuanbao.

628
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:51,330
We don't need to bother others.

629
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:55,600
Almost forgot.

630
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,800
Since you're already tutoring one,

631
00:30:58,800 --> 00:31:00,320
you might as well tutor two.

632
00:31:00,320 --> 00:31:01,650
Take our Qingyun along,

633
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:03,240
and tutor him too.

634
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:07,920
Yeah.

635
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,720
Mom, I don't need his tutoring.

636
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:13,480
What do you mean you don't need it?

637
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:16,080
Jingu hasn't even said if he wants to tutor you yet.

638
00:31:16,080 --> 00:31:17,280
Don't be ungrateful.

639
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:22,040
Sure, Auntie. I can do it.

640
00:31:23,720 --> 00:31:24,200
That's great.

641
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:25,480
Come on, eat up.

642
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:27,720
You can set the time.

643
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:29,360
Whenever you say you'll come,

644
00:31:29,360 --> 00:31:31,240
we'll start tutoring. Is that okay?

645
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:32,370
No problem, Auntie.

646
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:37,040
Okay, then I guess I have to thank you.

647
00:31:37,480 --> 00:31:39,040
Thank you, Meng.

648
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:40,760
You're welcome.
